        pages I used for chronicling our activities up till 2018 were a bit clunky to follow. Â </span><span style="font-size: 1em; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;">Just remember to pick the calendar quarter you're interested in and then remember that, like email, the most recent entriesÂ will be at the top. Each entry shows the relevant date. Â So the more recent dates are at the top of the first page,
        and those at the beginning of the quarter will be at the bottom of the last page.</span></p>
